sudo useradd -m <username>
sudo passwd <username>
sudo usermod -aG wheel username


chmod u+w filename  (Grants write permission to the file owner)
Replace filename with the actual filename. You can replace u+w with g+w for the group or o+w for others (use with caution!).

getent passwd list all user
whoami
who


